node.text:
WIthin seconds this car from @grouperenault transforms from its short City form in to its longer Travel form. The car lengthens by 40cm, which allows an extra battery pack to be inserted under the car for both its range and power to increase for longer trips. The long version also give passengers more leg room and space for bags in the back.
